  <h4>Hi <%= currentUser.name %> üé≠. Take a fews relaxing minutes to listen your sobbing soul üíÉüèª while API searching ... </h4>
  <a class="backBtn" href="/search"> &larr; Back </a>
  <br><br><br><br><br>
